<D>__{aspen. just got back. had a great time.}
<C>__{richie}
<D>__{i'd like to ski aspen some day.}
<C>__{tony}
<D>__{know who we met? burt reynolds. i'm not kidding. lot of people from hollywood go up there now, buying up everything.}
