<C>__{tony}
<D>__{i'm hoping you won't do that.}
<A>__{richie considers the room itself, measuring the odds of microphones and a recorder being in it somewhere.}
<C>__{tony}
<D>__{i'm not taping it. how do you know? because we're friends and i'm telling you. this is a real offer.}
